{"tid":161821,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"五點下午茶去吉野家食個火鍋面有咩要準備？","createTime":"2017-03-18T19:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T07:49:11.000Z","uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57c9d2daecc54cde9638e827c523d601a21fcb17","tid":161821,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3O9BY5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3O9BY5.gif&h=a498be2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吉野家食火鍋最緊要夠pot<br />\n一袋肉丸一袋菜心放上台面<br />\n咁大膽我已經瞪大曬眼，哎丫我坐多陣等到佢老公黎到，老婆仲話斬左個魚頭陣間放落去<br />\n免冷氣費煤氣費再免洗碗，一個下午茶食到晚飯時份，吉野家今次贏曬口碑真係抵讚"},{"pid":"5e32b54a05c3c0dd31d8b4af79919f430c251404","tid":161821,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:14:30.000Z","msg":"見過人拖隻牛入吉野家食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13737ac85b1a3e9d45f3d40dcbc6b706c53d7104","tid":161821,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:20:50.000Z","msg":"後面良心二字完美襯托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd7bf29c83e3d173f66ba13f8742a3f67ff3a9c","tid":161821,"uid":28998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:29:01.000Z","msg":"之前去食都見過有人自帶肥牛、丸、啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e169200f436c22ca71f4a658b82846daeeedc9d","tid":161821,"uid":65650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:29:14.000Z","msg":"天瑞鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"ab030edd9e4ff33d13fd772ba295d6446d83eb20","tid":161821,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:32:53.000Z","msg":"有電爐唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7faed143a9974f593fb89c8609a6748680da4414","tid":161821,"uid":66303,"lik